The src/prdc directory contains source files in namespace Pscf::Prdc that 
can by codes that are treat systems wtih periodic boundary conditions.

  - Classes in src/prdc/cpu are in nested namespace Pscf::Prdc::Cpu
  - Classes in src/prdc/cuda are in nested namespace Pscf::Prdc::Cuda

Subdirectories:

   crystal/  - unit cells, space groups, and symmetrized bases
   cpu/      - classes that define fields, only used on a CPU
   cuda/     - classes that define fields, only used on a GPU

